      • getArrayClass

        public static Class<?> getArrayClass​(Class<?> base,
                                     int dims)
        Get the array class with the given non-array base type and dimensions.
        Parameters:
        base - base type
        dims - number of dimensions
        Returns:
        the corresponding array type, or base if dims is zero
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if base is null
        IllegalArgumentException - if base is an array type
        IllegalArgumentException - if base is void and dims > 0
        IllegalArgumentException - if dims is not in the range 0..255
